          "book_id": "8A82C1696267E589CAC9B6E1E26D3AC1",
          "chapter": null,
          "text": "artist’s passion and a scientist's patience",
          "sentence": "If, however, a would-be reader is utterly devoid of passion and patience—of an artist’s passion and a scientist's patience—he will hardly enjoy great literature.",
          "note": null,
          "path": "epubcfi(/6/14[Section0005.xhtml]!/4/44/1,:427,:470)",
          "created_at": "2021-07-09 21:58:21 -0700",
